net.floodlightcontroller.dhcpserver

类 DHCPBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.dhcpserver.DHCPBinding

  • public class DHCPBinding
extends java.lang.Object
    The class representing a DHCP Binding -- MAC and IP. It also contains important information regarding the lease status --active --inactive the lease type of the binding --dynamic --fixed/static and the lease times --start time in seconds --duration in seconds
